<plot>A sniper is on the loose and so too is the spirit of Love... Angela Bettis and Kevin Ford are reunited in L2 to explore the final days of their country while on a road trip from Austin, Texas to Hollywood, California... with a brief dream visit to Spain! Along the way the pair interview many fellow citizens about the deadly situation brewing on the East Coast and run wild into their paranoid imaginations, leading to a very bloody return home to Los Angeles.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?346037</url></doc>
